column1: school: student's school (binary: 'GP' - Gabriel Pereira or 'MS' - Mousinho da Silveira).
gender: student's gender (binary: 'F' - female or 'M' - male)
age: student's age (numeric: from 15 to 22)
address: student's home address type (binary: 'U' - urban or 'R' - rural)
famsize: family size (binary: greater_than_3 or less_than_3).
parentstatus: parent's cohabitation status (binary: Apart or Together).
motheredu: mother's education (none
fatheredu: father's education (none
motherjob: mother's job (nominal: teacher
fatherjob: father's job (nominal: teacher
reason: reason to choose this school (nominal: close
guardian: student's guardian (nominal: mother
traveltime: home to school travel time (nominal: less_than_15min
studytime: weekly study time (nominal: less_than_2hr
failures: number of past class failures (numeric: 0
schoolsupport: extra educational support (binary: yes
famsupport: family educational support (binary: yes
extraclasses: extra paid classes within the course subject (binary: yes
extracurriculars: extra-curricular activities (binary: yes
attendednursery: attended nursery school (binary: yes
wantshigheredu: wants to take higher education (binary: yes
internetaccess: Internet access at home (binary: yes
romanticrel: with a romantic relationship (binary: yes
famrelrating:  quality of family relationships (numeric: from 1 - very bad to 5 - excellent).
freetimerating: free time after school (numeric: from 1 - very low to 5 - very high).
gooutrating: going out with friends (numeric: from 1 - very low to 5 - very high).
alcweekday: workday alcohol consumption (numeric: from 1 - very low to 5 - very high).
alcweekend: weekend alcohol consumption (numeric: from 1 - very low to 5 - very high).
healthrating: current health status (numeric: from 1 - very bad to 5 - very good).
absences: number of school absences (numeric: from 0 to 93).
